      • setManufacturerCertificates

        public EndorsementKeysTypes.Info.Builder setManufacturerCertificates(X509CertChain manufacturerCertificates)
        The TPM manufacturer's endorsement key certificate chain.

        Endorsement key certificates are signed by the TPM manufacturer. When available, the getManufacturerCertificates() property will contain the TPM manufacturer's endorsement key certificate chain.

        . This property was added in vSphere API 8.0.0.1. if null, the certificate chain is not available.
        Parameters:
        manufacturerCertificates - New value for the property.
